dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents the boundaries for the countries of the world at 1:15,000,000 scale. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.World Countries provides a basemap layer for the countries of the world. It has been designed to be used as a basemap that can be easily edited. Included are fields for name, ISO code, continent, and land type and rank.
